-- SNCB Revenue Dragged Down by Merchandise Transport, L’Echo Says
-- B y   G a s p a r d   S e b a g
-- 2013-06-29T09:00:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-29/sncb-revenue-dragged-down-by-merchandise-transport-l-echo-says.html
SNCB Holding SA’s revenue fell 2.3%
in the first quarter on shrinking earnings in the group’s
merchandise transport subsidiary, L’Echo reported today.
Belgium’s national railway sales decreased to 391.6 million
euros ($509 million) from 401 million euros last year, according
to accounts validated by the board and seen by L’Echo.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gaspard Sebag in Brussels at 
